data.title: Nobel Prize winning women
data.meta_description:
Since 1901, 60 women have been awarded a Nobel Prize. From first-ever winner Marie Curie to more recent winners, this gallery celebrates outstanding accomplishments in Chemistry, Physics, Medicine, Literature and Peace.

Curated by the Europeana XX project.
